  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Combine almond flour, piccalilli, egg, melted butter, honey, vanilla extract, and salt in a medium bowl, stirring until smooth.",
    "Stir in the raspberries and mix until they're evenly distributed throughout the mixture.",
    "Pour the mixture into a greased 6-inch round cake pan or a small ramekin."
